Equinoxe (Rus Equinox) - studio album by Jean Michel Jarre, released  1978.
Equinoxe recorded at the private studio of Jean-Michel Jarre on the equipment
Md-studio and on the Gang - studio (Paris) in 1978.

Disc concept is such his compositions are devoted to a specfic time of day,
from morning to night. Equinoxe is written without pauses between tracks,
track smoothly into one another (exception - the transition from the fourth to
the 5 - second part - the restriction "vinyl" format).
